            Setting the stage on fire with solo performances and group dances. Witness the passion and talent of our
            fresher participants as they captivate the audience with their mesmerizing moves and compelling
            storytelling.
          </p>

          <span class="circle"></span>
          <span class="time">7-8pm</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="title">Games Galore</h3>
          <p>
            A surprise awaits with a variety of exciting games! Engage in thrilling activities that promise fun and
            laughter for all. Don't miss out on the chance to join in the excitement!
          </p>

          <span class="circle"></span>
          <span class="time">8-8:30pm</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="title">Closing Event</h3>
          <p>
            The night will end with funny games and prize distribution. Concluding our festivities with joyous
            celebrations and recognition for outstanding performances. It's a finale you won't want to miss!
          </p>

          <span class="circle"></span>
          <span class="time">8:30-9pm</span>
        </li>
